graph TD
    style IN fill:#45B7D1,color:#000
    style R fill:#FFEAA7,color:#000
    style S fill:#4ECDC4,color:#000
    style E fill:#96CEB4,color:#000
    style A fill:#FF8C42,color:#000
    style G fill:#6C5CE7,color:#fff

    IN[Input Content\nfrom user or agent] --> R{RouterActor\nClassify intent\ntrack in Prometheus}
    R -->|summarize / short text| S[Summarize Pipeline\nChainActor]
    R -->|extract / entities| E[Extract Pipeline\nChainActor]
    R -->|analyze / compare| A[Analysis Pipeline\nChainActor]
    R -->|default| G[Generate Pipeline\nChainActor]
